{"tid":219051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦反釋法遊行，大量泛民被捕","createTime":"2017-04-27T03:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T13:03:11.000Z","uid":30807,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"414864e31ad6147ef3f9bb243ce734e412a7c1f2","tid":219051,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"來源：星火同盟抗爭支援<br />\n<br />\n【眾志成員再次被捕】(0900更新)<br />\n<br />\n今早七時，針對著中聯辦反釋法遊行，香港眾志常委林淳軒及林朗彥被上門拘捕，預計即將正式落案起訴他們參與非法集結及公眾地方行為不檢等罪名。<br />\n社民連吳文遠、周嘉發、陳文威、葉志衍，大專政關盧德昌，前嶺大學生會主席鄭沛倫同樣被捕。學聯前副秘書長王瀚樑則未能成功聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似未有人開po？"},{"pid":"0306a87212102b863e5c8cd3ff43daf747cad710","tid":219051,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"用呢兩條罪入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836ab7d99e9192007dd5e98f5c544b9b3157e5e3","tid":219051,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用呢兩條罪入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n萬能key"},{"pid":"9e4327f1ba936c38be34a18481004fc19bbc0653","tid":219051,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"【香港眾志兩常委等八人被捕 | 本土新聞】<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志和社民連分別在facebook指，最少有八人今早（廿七日）被警方拘捕，就去年十一月六日反釋法遊行事件被警方落案起訴，包括參與非法集結、公眾地方行為不檢等罪名。八人中，包括兩名香港眾志常委林淳軒及林朗彥；社民連主席吳文遠、副秘書長周嘉發、成員陳文威；大專政關葉志衍、盧德昌；前嶺南大學學生會會長鄭沛倫。學聯前常委王瀚樑則未能聯絡上，未知是否也被捕。（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n▋離地觀點橫行 香港要有《本土新聞》<br />\n▋訂閱方法<br />\n<br />\nPaypal: <a href=\"http://goo.gl/jfXV26\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjfXV26&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=1546c1a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/jfXV26</a><br />\n<br />\n或：東亞銀行戶口 015-254-68-00092-8 (Local Press Ltd) ，支票，ATM，網上過數均可。"},{"pid":"8f28c622a7452dd3c14370a0a592bc2bf0d4ce47","tid":219051,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"共匪開始清算"},{"pid":"2659b2e0c21452adc6bf52b1eaa6b2a79794f7ef","tid":219051,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:07:12.000Z","msg":"其實真係好撚痴線<br />\n<br />\n果日遊行分左兩條隊，有一條隊就激進d，有另一條隊就行完散水<br />\n<br />\n激進d果條路線係冇申請不反對通知書，但唔係個個都有做激進行為<br />\n<br />\n佢將所有人都拉哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b3773316fe2ed435b8b11b89eea3066d4f8ebd","tid":219051,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共匪開始清算</blockquote><br />\n大和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c4f55b9fd9d53e5c3f57cf067dcdfa31b96394","tid":219051,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>共匪開始清算</blockquote><br />\n大和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwe connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e31fcda8365703a3edf13b6cccf6595c2fbc1a8","tid":219051,"uid":29473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:10:50.000Z","msg":"建制狗：比次機會林鄭"},{"pid":"5469f4b1bb717cf09ff1766bbec35d2ecfbdfe97","tid":219051,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"前政務司長林鄭月娥以777票當選新任特首，民主黨主席胡志偉今早商台節目表示，民主黨會以「疑中留情」角度，看她用什麼方法重建社會信任、如何修補社會撕裂及隔絕與中聯辦關係、以及施政上是否站在香港人立場等 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0471fdfb5018b43ba6b0ef7b24c4e231a20613a","tid":219051,"uid"