sg":"乜都拉左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489a0fae292049ca3216475ed76cec1bf2381f08","tid":219051,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>共匪開始清算</blockquote><br />\n大和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對家而家完全強勢，又有薯片做中間派<br />\n可以直接收哂反對派皮"},{"pid":"28c38ba06a9c9ccad65a17d482fc06e645851f4f","tid":219051,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇法律撚可以講解下？<br />\n基本法話香港人有結社、集會自由<br />\n但又會有條非法集會<br />\n咁即係點？</blockquote><br />\n憲法一般寫得好general，細則先係5大法律<br />\n<br />\n情況等同基本法賦予言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n但相關法例，建基於呢條基本法下，如果言論涉及誹謗、恐嚇、危害公共秩序blah blah blah...都是犯法。"},{"pid":"14a0d94039a828af91b4cab16660c4215592998f","tid":219051,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇法律撚可以講解下？<br />\n基本法話香港人有結社、集會自由<br />\n但又會有條非法集會<br />\n咁即係點？</blockquote><br />\n憲法一般寫得好general，細則先係5大法律<br />\n<br />\n情況等同基本法賦予言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n但相關法例，建基於呢條基本法下，如果言論涉及誹謗、恐嚇、危害公共秩序blah blah blah...都是犯法。</blockquote><br />\n都係好自由, 咩都可以做, 只有2樣野唔準做.<br />\n<br />\n就係這也不準, 那也不準, 總之就好自由 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b9180ec2bdeb8491d3e0a1477e85884d0bdd59","tid":219051,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"其實穚枉過正唔係好事, 我敢講以後反對派唔犯任何法去抗爭, 港共政府仲頭痕.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n少左班廢既激進派, 但多左社會主流既中間派入反對派."},{"pid":"b3fb9a09cead586d6a54f906552976f90d8d539b","tid":219051,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d83e35ffb8093a501950df9bff808650c5774b4","tid":219051,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor